{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"14550-ramu-yagiye-kuroba","title":"Ramu yagiye kuroba","description":"Abashuti batatu baja kuroba : soma ibikurikira.","language":"Kinyarwanda","langCode":"rw","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"portrait","authors":["Noel Abaho"],"illustrators":["Soumya Menon"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Uganda Christian University","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/14550-ramu-yagiye-kuroba"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/721012/size3/1db7298d5b01da68f1fd305946c8895a.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/721012/size6/1db7298d5b01da68f1fd305946c8895a.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/612/size6/d585a09e6bf11692f42196b18fad83c6.jpg","text":"Ramu yabyutse mugitondo .yashakaga kuroba ifi.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/613/size6/a62ff49d8723f434ea3c112f74f0dd94.jpg","text":"Yarabonye Balu.Bakundaga gukina umunsii wose.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/614/size6/1872a0f12758631f33eb5560e699b75a.jpg","text":"Peeki nawe arababona. Baramubwira kobajana nawe.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/615/size6/a17fe8c8d4299296a20b95cb3b155be7.jpg","text":"Peeki aravuga, nimugyende nimba namazi ahari, ifi izaafa","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/616/size6/16e81ba16ebf463b73c2e2e8423f413d.jpg","text":"Nibunvishe Peeki kiya babwiye barakomeza kuja kuroba ifi","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/617/size6/4b69e07e9d38e4bd5d96425d68d2def8.jpg","text":"Ramu na Balu barabona ifi ibyiri. Agafi kamwe kari gatoya kandi indi yari nini.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/618/size6/5782ef630e94cebc84e4a13c5bf58824.jpg","text":"Ifi imwe indi iraza yari nini kyane kuruta zose.Peeki aravuga ngo ni nini kuruta ikigyeri kya Appa!","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/619/size6/46a13eb99ca4f964db1fffd13d48a9f7.jpg","text":"Bose barafatanya kuyikurura kuva mumazi.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/620/size6/960809a9d5d4819719d07ece4d3c2241.jpg","text":"Ramu na Baru bakomeza gushaka ifi","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/621/size6/4e421f61cdc1dff24f7e378ac0e1a792.jpg","text":"Indobani ziravunika Ramu agwa mumazi Baru agwa hansi.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/622/size6/403a852ae07f249ff6f855748dd596e1.jpg","text":"Ifi zi sigala mumazi zifite idobano mumimwa yazo.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":91}}